        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 1br Duplex- 950ft2 - Central location, park-like yard, great neighborhood, near Lake Como (StPaul Como Park) -nice lower duplex feels like a private home - approximately 950sqft -on-site owner/manager -quiet residential neighborhood with natural wildlife surroundings... visiting deer/ Bald Eagle and more. - in the heart of Como Park just east of Como Lake -near lake, park, golf course, skiing (cross country and small downhill), zoo, amusement park, pavilion/outdoor theater, , mini golf, Como Swimming Pool, Como Pavilion waterfall/ picnic areas, boat access/rentals, etc. -near walking/biking/roller blading trails (lake and park trails maintained year 'round by park services) -central location -close to 7+ local colleges/universities close to 3 major hospitals and numerous medical facilities -minutes to Hwys 94, 36, 35E/W, and short drive to St. Paul or Mpls downtown areas -enjoy a nice yard with limited garden space possible (free lawn service is provided - so no yardwork for you) -private three-season-porch/ small patio -larger shared-patio on property -garage (1 stall/with garage door opener) included in rent, plus plenty of open on-street parking -private laundry in basement, the washer and dryer is provided for you to use (free) -water, sewer, trash pickup IS included in rent -heat and electric are NOT included in rent, you must set up your own personal account billing with Xcel Energy -generous storage -onsite management - family owned, not corporate - Minimum 1-year Lease Firm -No smoking/No drugs/No waterbeds/ No candle/incense burning. Shown by appointment only - When scheduling the initial appointment by email please provide the names of anyone else (all) who will be renting with you. Prefer contact via text or phone. All persons who will rent should come to the appointment. This property is not licensed for Section 8, previous UD. References Required Must have great credit and work references, proof of stable employment or/income to cover expenses. Generally, one should demonstrate having an income of about 3 times the monthly rent. If you have your own credit score/info available (and printed out) this will save steps and save $ for you. The duplex is very close to East end of Lake Como, on Orange Ave.W. (mid-block, quiet, low-traffic street) near the N.W. intersection of Victoria St N and Orange Ave W. Willing to discuss other issues. You may also respond via email above and let me know your situation and ask further questions. Move-in flexibility may be negotiated. FOR FASTEST RESPONSE -- Text or call show contact info RENTAL FEATURES: - Natural Hardwood floors - Ceramic Tile Bath/Shower - Ceiling Fan + wall A.C. - Electric Stove - No dishwasher - Living room - Large dining room or multipurpose room - Enclosed 3-season porch, (private) with two additional patios (one shared) in yard - Basement (shared space) -Plus your own personal laundry area - for your unit only, with free use of washer/dryer - Yard - one private Patio - one shared patio - no yardwork (lawn service maintains) - Cable ready throughout (you will need your own subscription, however) - Garage (1-car garage space included in rent - garage door opener) DETAILED DESCRIPTION: One BR lower duplex located in Como Park neighborhood. Clean, well maintained home with on-site owner/manager. Located in a beautiful quiet, residential area, large yard, lots of wildlife. It's just a short walk or bike ride to Como Lake, Park, Golf Course, Zoo, many trails, the conservatory, pavilion/live theater, Como swimming pool, Como amusement park. Convenient to entertainment, shopping and dining, a short drive to 7+ local colleges and universities (U of M, Hamline/Mitchell School of Law, Macalester, St Thomas, Northwestern, St Paul College, Metro State, Century College....and minutes from Hwys 94/36/35E/W, 10 minutes to downtown St. Paul, close to 3 major hospitals/ medical services. This is in a prime central location. The apartment has generous closet space and storage, patio, large partially enclosed yard with lawn service included. Rent includes 1-car garage space Personal washer/dryer free to use; Rent does NOT include heat or electricity. No smoking/No drugs/No waterbeds, no burning of candles or incense. Minimum 1-yr lease Start Aug 1st / check other options Security deposit required - equal to one month's rent. We will screen ALL REFERENCES/ to prove Work history/ rental history/ credit history etc for each occupant. No Application Fee (Except - unless needed for additional credit/rent/background/work history checks.",
