        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Two months rent free on select units. Welcome to Lyndy Apartments Beds: Studio Baths: 1 Square Feet: 492 Use this link for more information: https://ipg.aptdetails.com/tls68d Welcome to Lyndy - Downtown Minneapolis Apartments Call Now - show contact info x 22 OR Text 22 to show contact info to text our team directly.   Community Info Live in luxury at Lyndy Apartments! Whether youre looking for a studio, 1 bedroom or 2 bedroom apartment home, youll fall in love with our sleek finishes and fixtures, large windows, beautiful common areas, fitness center and the incredible views from our very own sky lounge and rooftop patio. Lyndy Apartments is conveniently located in Downtown Minneapolis in the Lyn-Lake neighborhood, a lively neighborhood that is home of muralists, coffee shops and lots of unique food options. Call or stop by today for a tour! Residence Features ✩  Microwave ✩  Cable Ready ✩  View ✩  Refrigerator ✩  Disposal* ✩  Washer/Dryer ✩  Large Closets ✩  Patio/Balcony ✩  Water, Sewer, Trash, Gas, Electricity & Internet Included* ✩  Air Conditioner ✩  Hardwood Floors ✩  Dishwasher Community Features ✩  Meeting Room ✩  Sky Lounge ✩  Heated Parking Garage ✩  Fitness Center ✩  Pet Friendly ✩  Roof Top Patio ✩  Convenient Access to Greenway ✩  BBQ/Picnic Area ✩  Beautiful Common Areas Pet Policy Cats and Dogs Allowed - 2 Max. Breed restrictions apply. Pet Fee and Deposit are each $300. Pet Rent is $45 per pet per month. Office Hours Tuesday-Saturday: 8:00AM-5:00PM Equal Housing Opportunity jrq6oqqjN1",
