        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Up to 2 months free on select apartments! Apply within 24 hours of showing for additional specials! Reduced App fee down to $35.00!! This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, Approximately 855 Sq. Ft. Interested In This Unit? Use this link for more details: https://ipg.aptdetails.com/tqtzv1 Call Now - show contact info x 29 OR Text 29 to show contact info to text our team directly. ELEVATE COMFORT. ELEVATE LIFESTYLE. Community Info: Redefine your standards and take life in Downtown West Minneapolis to the next level at ELEVATE Apartment Homes. Our spacious one- and two-bedroom apartments offer more than enough space to serve as the canvas for your perfect lifestyle. While enjoying your morning coffee with panoramic views of the horizon becomes a new ritual and impromptu gatherings on our rooftop Sun Deck create lasting memories. Here, we are not just about elevating your home; we strive to elevate your community, your comfort, and your lifestyle. We take the everyday moments and elevate them into something special. Whether you want to sweat it out in our well-appointed fitness center, strike up a friendly competition on our rooftop Sports Deck, or enjoy a relaxing soak year-round in our indoor pool. Our community is teeming with opportunities for work and play. From conveniences like our business center to unique perks like our steam room and spaces to share like our community room, we've thought of everything so you can focus on what truly matters. Features: ‣  Wheelchair Access ‣  Central Heating/Air ‣  All-In-One Washer/Dryer ‣  Carpeting ‣  Black GE Appliance Package ‣  Patio/Balcony* ‣  Fully Equipped Kitchen ‣  Refrigerator ‣  Large Closets ‣  Granite Countertops ‣  Microwave ‣  Disposal ‣  Dishwasher ‣  Window Coverings ‣  Cable Ready ‣  Plank Flooring Community Amenities: ‣  Bike Racks ‣  Free Weights ‣  Parking Garage ‣  Spa/Hot Tub ‣  Controlled Access/Gated ‣  Concierge ‣  Recycling ‣  Basketball Court ‣  Night Patrol ‣  24 Ho