        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Two months rent free on select units. Lyndy Apartments 2905 Harriet Ave S, Minneapolis, MN, 55408 Need more information? Copy this link: https://ipg.aptdetails.com/jeb03s Call Now - show contact info x 21 OR Text 21 to show contact info to text with us. Welcome to Lyndy - Downtown Minneapolis Apartments 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath | Approximately 956 Sq. Ft. Community Info: Welcome to Lyndy Apartments, where we've reimagined the concept of community living to align seamlessly with your desires for comfort, leisure, and entertainment. Nestled in Minneapolis, MN, our pet-friendly apartments redefine what it means to feel at home, offering an unparalleled blend of prime location and exciting amenities. Whether you choose a studio, one-, two-, or three-bedroom apartment, you'll benefit from a host of convenient features and services that will make your day a breeze. Revel in the convenience of in-unit washers and dryers, and heated garage parking, all while knowing the second you arrive on the property, our on-site management and maintenance teams are ready to assist you. Feel convenience at your fingertips as utility management is long gone, since utilities are included at these Minneapolis apartments. When you're ready to find some well-deserved relaxation and recreation, come and enjoy our community amenities! Lounge at the rooftop patio with new neighbors or hit the fitness center to melt the stress from your workday away. When you're done, return to your new home, complete with plank flooring and captivating city views.   Unit Highlights ✧  Cable Ready ✧  Dishwasher ✧  Microwave ✧  Washer/Dryer ✧  Patio/Balcony ✧  Water, Sewer, Trash, Gas, Electricity & Internet Included* ✧  Disposal* ✧  Refrigerator ✧  Air Conditioner ✧  Large Closets ✧  View ✧  Hardwood Floors Community Highlights ✧  BBQ/Picnic Area ✧  Beautiful Common Areas ✧  Convenient Access to Greenway ✧  Heated Parking Garage ✧  Fitness Center ✧  Meeting Room ✧  Roof 