        "locality": "Minneapolis",
        "geocode_query": "1117 Marquette Ave., Minneapolis",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Up to 2 months free on select apartments! Apply within 24 hours of showing for additional specials! Reduced App fee down to $35.00!! Elevate Apartment Homes 1117 Marquette Ave., Minneapolis, MN, 55403 Call Now - show contact info x 28 OR Text 28 to show contact info to text our leasing team. Want more information on this unit? See link (below): https://ipg.aptdetails.com/vlw0us ELEVATE COMFORT. ELEVATE LIFESTYLE. 1 bedroom | 1 bath | 742 square feet Features ✓  All-In-One Washer/Dryer ✓  Fully Equipped Kitchen ✓  Granite Countertops ✓  Black GE Appliance Package ✓  Patio/Balcony* ✓  Wheelchair Access ✓  Plank Flooring ✓  Cable Ready ✓  Large Closets ✓  Window Coverings ✓  Disposal ✓  Refrigerator ✓  Central Heating/Air ✓  Carpeting ✓  Microwave ✓  Dishwasher Community Features ✓  High Speed Internet ✓  Outdoor BBQ and Lounge Area ✓  Tennis / Pickleball Court ✓  Elevator ✓  Controlled Access/Gated ✓  Recycling ✓  1st Floor Social Lounge ✓  24 Hour Emergency Maintenance ✓  Downtown Minneapolis Location ✓  On-Site Management ✓  Concierge ✓  Spa/Hot Tub ✓  7th Floor Social Lounge ✓  Laundry Facilities ✓  Direct Skyway Access ✓  Night Patrol ✓  Parcel Lockers ✓  Bike Racks ✓  Water, Sewer, Trash, Gas and Steam Included ✓  7th Floor Sundeck ✓  Business Center ✓  Fitness Center ✓  Parking Garage ✓  Free Weights ✓  Basketball Court ✓  Pet Washing Station ✓  Indoor Swimming Pool ✓  Off Street Parking Community Info Redefine your standards and take life in Downtown West Minneapolis to the next level at ELEVATE Apartment Homes. Our spacious one- and two-bedroom apartments offer more than enough space to serve as the canvas for your perfect lifestyle. While enjoying your morning coffee with panoramic views of the horizon becomes a new ritual and impromptu gatherings on our rooftop Sun Deck create lasting memories. Here, we are not just about elevating your home; we strive to elevate your community, your comfort, and your lifestyle. We take the everyday moments and elevate them into something special. Whether you want to sweat it out in our well-appointed fitness center, strike up a friendly competition on our rooftop Sports Deck, or enjoy a relaxing soak year-round in our indoor pool. Our community is teeming with opportunities for work and play. From conveniences like our business center to unique perks like our steam room and spaces to share like our community room, we've thought of everything so you can focus on what truly matters. Pet Policy Cats and Dogs Allowed - 2 Max. Breed restrictions apply. Pet Fee and Deposit are each $300. Pet Rent is $45 per pet per month. Income Requirements 2.5 x the asking rent Office Hours Monday-Saturday: 9:00AM-6:00PM Sunday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Equal Housing Opportunity POL1J5ptxtR",
