        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Available now. Not the whole house, just the lower unit in this duplex. Convenient location 2xxx Girard ave N, Minneapolis Mn 55411 Brand new carpet and fresh paint. 4 bedroom/ 1bathroom, forced air heating. Very close to school and public transport/bike path. Laundry and extra storage space in basement. Tenant is responsible for lawn care and snow. Parking/Storage: street parking available for free, also one offstreet parking in the back. Lease Term: 12 + Months Utilities Included in Rent: Water/Sewer and Trash Utilities Paid By Tenant: Electricity and gas Qualifications: Must have satisfactory rental history, must pass criminal history background check and must have documented income of 3 times the monthly rent. Past 2 landlord references (mandatory) required. No evictions or criminal records. Section 8 accepted (1x for section 8). No application fee but $40 non-refundable fee for background check using third party app once you are confirmed. 1 month rent as security deposit and one month advance rent.",
