        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome to 708 Holly Ave, a charming apartment located in the heart of Saint Paul, MN in the desirable Summit-University neighborhood. Only blocks from the historic Summit Ave and Grand Ave, this open and inviting space offers modern and comfortable living in a convenient location. Features: Warm and welcoming living room with high ceilings and plenty of natural light Large kitchen with eat-in dining Relax in spacious bedroom with ample closet space Unwind on your own private deck Updated bathroom with stylish fixtures In-building washer and dryer for added convenience Enjoy classic wood trim original to this historic building. Off street parking space available Located in a vibrant neighborhood, you'll be within walking distance to local pubs, shops, restaurants, parks, and public transportation options. Experience the best of Saint Paul living at 708 Holly Ave! Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity. Schedule a viewing today! Rental Terms Rent: $1250 Available: 9/1/26 (Minimum 1 year lease) Application Fee: $40.00 per adult Security Deposit: 1 month's rent Renter responsible for utilities MUST HAVE REFERENCES from previous landlords. Background and credit checks required No Smoking Cats allowed Dogs not allowed 2 max occupants",
