        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post This is a 1 bedroom 1 bathroom apartment in an 8-unit building, back to a city park with ball fields. Convenient and central location. Near Mall of America (MOA), MSP airport, VA Hospital, Eagan outlet mall, and many businesses. Quick Access to Hwy 62 & 77. On bus line to downtown Minneapolis and University of Minnesota. Bossen Field Park is less than 1 block from the building, offers wading pool, paly structure, baseball, soccer fields. Blocks away from Lake Nokomis. 1 year lease. Rent covers water, heating, cooking gas, trash, lawn/snow care. Tenant is responsible for electricity. Qualification Guideline: credit 650+; no recent criminal history; good rental history. Handy person is welcome, and gets the opportunity to do repair and work on small projects in exchange of rent credit. Maximum number of residents: 2 adult (an additional young child is okay). security Deposit: 1 month rent.",
