        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post 250th Anniversary Special: $1,000 off your first month rent. Special ends July 31st. Washer/Dryer is at your front door of this private entry townhome apartment. Walnut stained Shaker cabinets and vanities. Granite countertops in kitchen and baths. Stainless steel appliances. Porcelain hardwood floors! White enameled doors and trim! A very special upscale look! Each apartment also features a computer station in the kitchen, a private deck or patio, ample storage, and a cozy wood fireplace in select apartments! Experience the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in our beautifully renovated townhome-style apartments. We're cat-friendly to your neute red or spayed cat! 1 and 2 bedroom townhome apartments from $1,349 to $1,609. Water and trash service from $30 to $50. Application fee: $50 Deposit: $1,300 Cat deposit: $500 Cat rent: $50 Admin: $200 Garage: Included in rent. Schedule a tour: email or call show contact info Apply online: walnuttrailsapartments.com. Rental Office: 9:00 AM to 6:00 PM daily; 10:00 AM to 4:00 PM Saturdays. 1813 Trailway Drive Eagan, MN 55122",
