        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Ask how to get 1/2 off Security Deposit. * *This offer is subject to change without notice. This is a Studio , 1 Bath, Approximately 400 Sq. Ft. See our property details here: https://ipg.aptdetails.com/porf70 Call Now - show contact info x 172 OR Text 172 to show contact info to text our team directly. Welcome Home! Community Info: Blaisdell Apartments is proud to offer a personable, caring, and service-oriented rental opportunity. Our 5 conveniently located, inner city apartment buildings have been completely modernized. We are eager to offer upgraded apartment homes at an affordable price to our fellow lovers of city living. Our community is nestled in the heart of the Whittier Neighborhood along Blaisdell Ave. and is just blocks from Eat Street, Downtown & Uptown Minneapolis. Blaisdell Apartments is conveniently located nearby major bus routes. We know that you’ll find the perfect style to suit your needs here. Please call for further details as Income Restrictions Apply. Features: ‣  Call Today ‣  1 & 2 BR Available ‣  Fully Equipped Kitchens with Dishwasher ‣  Air Conditioning & Central Heating ‣  Tech Ready ‣  Completely Upgraded Homes ‣  Ceiling Fans ‣  Whittier Neighborhood Close to Eat Street Community Amenities: ‣  On-Site Management ‣  On-Site Maintenance ‣  Laundry Facilities on site Income Requirements: 1.5 times the monthly rent Office Hours: Monday-Friday: 8:00AM-5:00PM Blaisdell Apartments 2200 Blaisdell Ave. S, Minneapolis, MN, 55404 Equal Housing Opportunity c0D6TsmHYLJb",
