        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Convenient location, close to MOA shopping, and highway 62, 77. On bus line. Walk to Bossen Field park, where you can find play structure, wading pool, and multiple ball fields. Blocks away from Lake Nokomis. Apartment is on the garden level. Carpet has been replaced with LVP flooring. Rent covers water, heating, cooking gas, trash, lawn/snow care, and parking spot behind the building. Tenant is responsible for electricity. 1 year lease. Qualification Guideline: credit 600+; no recent criminal history; good rental history; income 2.5 times rent. Handy person is welcome, and gets the opportunity to do maintenance & repair in exchange of rent credit. Maximum number of residents: 4. security Deposit: 1 month rent.",
