        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Studio / 1ba - $1,095.00 a mo. Oakmont Apartments is located in the Twin Cities suburb of Coon Rapids. You will enjoy our quiet neighborhood and the convenience of our close proximity to Riverdale Shopping Center and much more. Our beautiful property is just minutes Hwy 610, Hwy10, and Hwy 169. Within walking distance to Mercy Hospital and just a short drive to Main St. Anoka. Studio / 1ba - $1,095.00 - Security Deposit same as Rent amount Enjoy the ability to apply, pay your rent, and pay for laundry all on-line!!! In addition to a picnic area on property, we are within walking distance to many outdoor trails and Coon Rapids Dam Regional Park. This park easily accommodates year-round activities, which include biking, boating, fishing, hiking, and cross-country skiing. Contact us to schedule a visit at Oakmont Apartments today! You'll enjoy all your new home has to offer. Unique Features: Patio/Balcony Dine-In Kitchen Walk-In Closet Air Conditioner BBQ/Picnic Area Community Amenities Laundry Facilities Recycling Off Street Parking Location is close to: Riverdale Shopping Center Coon Rapids Dam Regional Park Mercy Hospital/Medical Campus Administrative Fee $0 Application Fee $35 Details- Lease Options 1yr - then a 60 day notice to vacate Security Deposit- Equal to one month's rent - could be higher, depends on screening results. Property Information 48 units/3 stories Location: Oakmont Apartments 11610 Tulip St NW, Coon Rapids, MN 55433 Coon Rapids, MN 55433 Contact : show contact info / Kim https://esoxmgmt.managebuilding.com/Resident/public/home Copy and paste link into your browser to apply online: https://esoxmgmt.managebuilding.com/Resident/rental-application/new Equal Housing Opportunity",
