        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Enjoy this amazing second floor condominium in the highly sought after Grand Condominiums located in Excelsior & Grand! This southern facing, bright home features: 10 ft. ceilings, open floor plan; floor-to-ceiling windows; wood floors; expansive 10' kitchen island with granite countertops & comfortable seating for 4; a 9'10\" x 10'11\" den with French doors; primary bedroom featuring a bathroom ensuite with double sinks, separate soaking tun and private shower/toilet room; laundry room with full size washer and dryer; 1 underground heated parking space with private storage room, available EV charging capability The Grand's amenities include outdoor pool & hot tub, fire pit, BBQ gas grills, fitness room, community room & guest suite. Adjacent to Wolfe Park with walking & biking trails, pickleball courts, live music, picnic areas, playgrounds, St. Louis Park Rec Center. Experience all that E&G has to offer all within walking distance: grocers, coffee shops, breweries, access to lakes & preserve nature areas, shopping and future light rail.",
