        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post $2,840/month 1687 s/f 3 Beds, 2 Full and 1 Half Baths Parking: 2-Car Attached Garage Lease Duration: 12 Months Deposit: $500 Pets Policy: Dogs and Cats Ok Laundry: In Unit We invite you to step inside a world of comfort, a place defined by style, substance and sustainability. Our homes and townhomes for rent in Maple Grove bring impressive floor plans alongside excellent amenities and professional services at your fingertips. With unique luxury layouts available, our houses and townhomes are crafted with high-end materials and finishes ensuring your wellbeing at all turns. It starts from the reinforced foundation, community irrigation systems and steel garage doors. Inside your new home you will find quality fixtures, LVP flooring, efficient brand new appliances and much more. Your new kitchen is equally impressive with granite countertops and stained cabinets, while the stylish bathrooms will make every day feel like a spa day. Our community also features well-lighted sidewalks, a mailbox station and a dedicated management team ready to help with anything you might need for added peace of mind. Complementing the appeal of our Maple Grove homes for rent is our excellent location. Enjoy living with easy access to Highway 610, 169 & 94 with just moments away from popular parks and shopping centers. HOME AMENITIES Granite kitchen countertops Stainless steel appliance package Modern gray shaker cabinets Wood inspired flooring throughout Quartz bathroom countertops Plush carpet with pad on stairs Ample closet space Fiberglass shower in master suite; fiberglass shower/tub combo in guest bathroom Window Coverings SmartCode locks Washer and dryer in laundry room Attached garage for convenient home access Dog Park Snow removal included Lawn care included Mike Miller/Licensed Agent Equal Housing Opportunity. Prices and availability are subject to change.",
