        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Contact info: Toni Hill | The Apartment Resource | show contact info 1Br/1Ba - Garage Parking Included, Built-In Wine Rack, Two-Tone Paint, Rooftop Sport Court, In/Outdoor Resort-Style Pools! Hwy 394, Golden Valley, MN 55416 $1730/mo KEY FEATURES Sq Footage: 729 sqft. Bedroom: 1 Bathroom: 1 Parking: One Heated Garage Spot Included, $75/2nd Garage Spot, Complimentary Surface Lot Parking Lease Duration: 12 Months Deposit: $500 Pets Policy: Cats & Dogs OK (30lb Max) Laundry: In Unit Property Type: Apartment DESCRIPTION Experience Uptown Living In Our Minneapolis Apartments BRAND NEW! NOW LEASING for July 31st Move-In! - Ultra-Luxury resort-style apartments designed to check all of the boxes on your list! We are a pet friendly community, close to the Shops at West End and just 10 minutes from downtown Minneapolis. Wait until you see our power-packed interiors and exceptional amenities! We combine service and style to create apartment living unlike any other in the Twin Cities. This truly is, luxury at its finest! Prices and availability are subject to change. IN-HOME AMENITIES Soaring 10-Foot or 11-Foot Ceilings Throughout Digital Front Entry Locks Front-Loading Washers & Dryers in Every Home Soft Loft Styles Signature Porcelain Floors Patio Fireplaces Granite Countertops Frosted Glass Doors Individual Water Heaters USB Charging Ports Textured Walls with Two-Tone Paint Towering 8-Foot Doors Throughout Built-In Buffets with Granite Slab Tops Intrusion Alarms with Motion Detection Private Terraces & Patios Built-In Wine Racks Frameless Glass Walk-In Showers with Separate Soaking Tubs Expansive Kitchen Islands Corner Two-Way Exposure Designer Tile Backsplashes Stainless Appliances Ice & Water Dispensing Refrigerators Smooth Glass Top Ranges Wine Refrigerators Custom Home Cabinetry Bedrooms to Accommodate King-Size Beds and Dressers Dressing Rooms, Closets and Seasonal Storage Granite Slab Vanity Tops Undermount Sinks COMMUNITY AMENITIES Boutique-Style Community Skydeck Lounge Rooftop Sport Courts Indoor Exercise Pool State-of-the-Art Health Club Luxurious Outdoor Pool with Poolside Cabanas and Inviting Sun Terrace Attached Heated Parking Garage Electric Vehicle Charging Stations Creative Studio Elevators Outdoor Entertainment Lounge with Grilling Stations Cyber Café with Wi-Fi Manicured Gardens Carpeted Climate-Controlled Corridors Walk Score® 59 Concierge Package Lockers Off-Leash Dog Park Guest Suite Accommodations Contact info: Mike Miller The Apartment Resource show contact info Equal Housing Opportunity",
