        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post $2900/month 1382 s/f Bedrooms: 3 Bathrooms: 2 2-Car Attached Garage Lease Duration: 12 Months Deposit: $1250 Pets Policy: Dogs & Cats OK Laundry: In Unit Our beautifully designed single-family home rental community offers the perfect blend of comfort, privacy, and convenience. Just 20 minutes east of St. Paul, this new construction neighborhood provides the feel of home with the ease of maintenance-free living. Enjoy the space and independence of a single-family home while benefiting from thoughtful shared amenities like a community clubhouse, fitness center, and outdoor pool—all designed to support your lifestyle without the upkeep. This home features 3-bedrooms and 2-bathrooms in a thoughtfully designed single-level floorplan. Enjoy the light-filled and open-concept layout with convenient access to the home's private rear patio directly off the dining room. The kitchen boasts high-end finishes such as stainless-steel appliances, solid surface countertops, soft-close cabinets, gas range, counter island, pantry closet and modern accent lighting. The living room's gas fireplace (with built-in decorative mantel) adds ambiance and coziness to the entire home. The primary bedroom features an en suite bathroom, with walk-in shower and double sinks, and a generously sized walk-in closet. Other conveniences include centrally located washer and dryer, attached 2-car garage and entry way coat closet. Our Community offers the privacy and pride of single home living while enjoying the hassle-free convenience of renting. Equal Housing Opportunity. Prices and availability are subject to change. Live comfortably. Live connected. Welcome home. RESIDENT FEATURES Home Amenities Attached 2-car garage (EV charger-ready) Butler's pantry* Mudroom* Stainless steel appliances Gas range Quartz countertops Soft close cabinets and drawers Walk-in closets Dual-bathroom vanities Walk-in shower and full bath in each home Washer and dryer Private patio Basement storage* Gas fireplace with mantel Ceiling fans Professionally maintained landscaping *Available in select plans Community Amenities On-site management team 24/7 maintenance Lawncare Snow removal 24/7 Fitness Center Exclusive community events Contact: Mike Miller / Licensed Agent show contact info",
