        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Spacious 1-bedroom upper-level duplex, potentially convertible to a 1-bedroom with a smaller living space, located near the YMCA and Blaisdell Bike Lane in the Lyndale/Uptown area. Features include in-unit laundry, ample attic storage, a shared garage, off-street parking, and a large elevated deck. Pet-friendly with additional fees. Available for rent at $520 (security deposit also $520) starting 7/15 or 8/1, with a 12-month lease. The application requires a $65 fee per adult, a background check, and proof of income (3 times the rent). Tenants cover gas and electric utilities; the owner pays for water, sewer, garbage, lawn, and snow removal. Managed by Associated Property Services. Please text me your number so I can send the details.",
