        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Bedrooms:  1 Bathrooms:  1 Square Feet:  605 Date Available:  2026-06-17 Address:  1301 MN-7 Welcome to Brentwood Park, where comfort meets convenience! Our thoughtfully designed floor plans cater to a variety of lifestyles. Whether you're looking for a cozy one-bedroom or a roomy townhome, you'll find the perfect home to suit your needs. Explore our floor plans and discover why Brentwood Park is the ideal place to call home. Amenities Include: Off-Street Parking Eat-in Kitchen Pre-installed blinds Generous Sized Storage Sleek Kitchen Finishes Easy Access to Public Transportation Extra Storage (Apartments) Laundry Facility on Site Hopkins School District Flex Rental Payments Available Durable Flooring Divided sink Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://thegoodmangroupliving.com/hsobkush/brentwood-park Pricing and availability are subject to change.A non-refundable application of fee of $45 is due at time of applying for apartment home. A non-refundable administration fee of $129 is due at time of move in. This community utilizes a Ratio Utility Billing Service (RUBS). Residents are responsible for payment of the following utilities: Electric, Gas, Water, Sewer, and Trash. Residents must pay a non-refundable RUBS billing fee of $4.08 per month, in addition to the resident’s portion of the property’s utilities for which resident is responsible.",
