        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post This large 4BR 2-story single family house is located in the heart of trendy NE Minneapolis, just half a mile east of Central Avenue and minutes from downtown Minneapolis. The area features new tap rooms and artist lofts. - 4 Bedrooms, 2 Bath - Central air conditioning - Beautiful oak hardwood floors in 2 bedrooms, carpet in the other 2 bedrooms - Off-street parking for multiple vehicles (no garage) - Bedroom sizes: 12x12, 12x11, 11x11, 11x10 Monthly rent is $1,700 for the first month (special), with regular rent at $1,775. Available for move-in on the 1st or 15th of the upcoming month. Strict limit of 5 total occupants. Clean criminal and rental history required. No application fee. This is a new posting, and the first showings will begin soon. Please schedule an appointment to view the property. Feel free to reply with a valid phone number and your preferred move-in date so we can follow up.",
