        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Large Studio Great Location! Hrdwd flrs, River views 5 min to downtown 196 Mounds Blvd, Unit 6B, Saint Paul, MN 55106 995.00 / Month BEDROOMS | 1 BATHROOMS Interested? Fill out this form : https://renter.turbotenant.com/general-prescreener/T3duZXI6NjY3MTM2?property=1254796&source=cl Have questions? Contact the Landlord : https://rental.turbotenant.com/p/196-mounds-blvd-saint-paul-mn-unit-unit-6b/0e54e9a5-188f-401e-bc1b-23e65af1b507?source=craigslist Property Description: Step into timeless charm and modern comfort in this spacious 1BR nestled in a stately 1880s mansion—directly across from Indian Mounds Park with stunning river and city views. Soak in the beauty of our shared front porch or unwind beneath soaring ceilings and gleaming hardwood floors. Studio unit in the 2nd floor of our 3-storey building, perfect for 1–2 guests. One small pet allowed (subject to approval). Unfurnished—style it your way. Only 5 minutes to downtown St. Paul and 2 minutes to Metro State. Enjoy walkable access to Waḳaƞ Ṭípi Sanctuary, Wabasha Street Caves, Science Museum, Ordway, Lowertown, and more. Quiet corner location with free, easy street parking. Shared washer/dryer in basement. Security camera at entrance for peace of mind. Tenant sets up electricity and WiFi. Gas, water/sewer, trash/recycling billed back monthly. Love where you live—message us today to schedule a tour! We'll upload more photos after doing further improvements. Property Type : Apartment Pets : Cats, Small Dogs, Large Dogs Allowed Smoking : OUTSIDE_ONLY Lease Term : 995.00 / Month 995.00 Deposit Lease Length: One Year Available: 07/01/2025 Occupancy Limit: 2 People Utilities Included : Appliances : Dishwasher Washer Dryer Refrigerator Amenities : Near Parks Lawn On Site Laundry Security Cameras Heating & Cooling : Other Wall Interested? Fill out this form : https://renter.turbotenant.com/general-prescreener/T3duZXI6NjY3MTM2?property=1254796&source=cl Have question