        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post June Special: Move in during the month of June and get one month FREE! *only applicable on 1-bedrooms. 1423 11th Avenue South, Minneapolis, MN 55404 Conveniently located in downtown Minneapolis, this stunning community allows our residents to live a vibrant lifestyle - all within blocks of major restaurants, theatres, and shopping! East Village Apartments offers a variety of floor plans with spacious kitchens equipped with energy-efficient appliances, large windows offering wonderful views of the city, beautifully landscaped grounds, and washer and dryer in each apartment! Amenities Include: Oak Cabinets and Woodwork Courtyard Low Ply Carpet - Hypo-allergenic Private Porch Entrances in some Units Washer and Dryer Large Closets Storage Lockers ($20/month) 7-Day Security Patrol Window Treatments Provided Private Courtyard Cable Ready Bike Storage Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://liveaeon.org/hxzaqshf/east-village *Pricing and availability are subject to change daily. Photos may not be of the exact advertised apartment. Please contact us today for the most updated information. Professionally managed by Aeon, a provider of Fair housing and Equal Opportunity",
