        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Luxurious 3Bed 3Bath Townhouse - Private Backyard Unit in Rogers | $2650/mo 127xx Ashbury Dr, Rogers, MN 55374 2650.00 / Month 3 BEDROOMS | 3 BATHROOMS Interested? Fill out this form : https://renter.turbotenant.com/general-prescreener/T3duZXI6NzU5NTMz?property=2454405&source=cl Have questions? Contact the Landlord : https://rental.turbotenant.com/p/127xx-ashbury-dr-rogers-mn/ff29c62e-fbe4-4069-95eb-1d574b83514b?source=craigslist Property Description: Experience luxury in this brand-new unit nestled in the scenic rolling hills of the Big Woods community, this home offers the perfect \"country meets metro\" lifestyle PREMIUM FEATURES -- Artistic design with natural light from large windows, privacy blinds, and featuring a gorgeous private backyard with tranquil pond (see pics) -- 3-Bedroom configuration plus a versatile loft perfect for a home office or playroom. Centrally located upper-level laundry and a large 2-car attached garage -- Luxury Primary Suite with a private bathroom featuring a large walk-in closet -- Gourmet Kitchen with quartz countertops, stainless-steel appliances, and whole house water softener -- Smart Home: Integrated video doorbell, smart lock, and more -- Schools: Highly regarded Rogers School (10/10) OWNER-PAID SERVICES ($446/month VALUE !) -- Professional Lawn Care & Landscaping -- Snow Removal (from your driveway!) -- Utility Tune Up & Maintenance (For Energy Efficiency) -- Appliances Repair Plan (Total peace of mind) -- Trash & Exterior Maintenance UNBEATABLE DAILY CONVENIENCE, ELITE RECREATION & LIFESTYLE (All within 10 mins!) Prime Location: Perfectly near I-94 for seamless access and convenience to SuperTarget, CVS Pharmacy, Starbucks, Dunkin, Cub Foods, Walgreens, Dining & \"Quick Bites\", Main Street Rogers, Wells Fargo, TruStone Financial, 21st Century Bank, UPS Store, local drycleaners, and automotive services Nature & Activity: Minutes from Crow-Hassan Park Reserve (2,600 acres of trails), Henry’s Woods (historic 50-acre forest with \"Sugar Shack\"), hiking/horseback trails, a premier off-leash dog area and Hassan Meadow Park (disc golf/sports fields) Activity: Quick access to Fieldhouse (indoor turf, free resident track, and ice arena) SCREENING Income: Min 2.5x monthly rent. Pets: $0 rent. Case-by-case approval with deposit Credit score: 700+ w/ clean background Co-applicants: Low/short credit history may require a risk-mitigating deposit Property Type : Townhouse Pets : Cats, Small Dogs, Large Dogs Allowed Smoking : OUTSIDE_ONLY Lease Term : 2650.00 / Month 2650.00 Deposit Lease Length: One Year Available: 08/01/2026 Occupancy Limit: 5 People Utilities Included : Garbage Recycling Appliances : Dishwasher Dryer Refrigerator Washer Microwave Range Oven Amenities : Alarm System Cable Ready Near Parks Lawn Fireplace Wired For Internet Heating & Cooling : Forced Air Central Interested? Fill out this form : https://renter.turbotenant.com/general-prescreener/T3duZXI6NzU5NTMz?property=2454405&source=cl Have questions? Contact the Landlord : https://rental.turbotenant.com/p/127xx-ashbury-dr-rogers-mn/ff29c62e-fbe4-4069-95eb-1d574b83514b?source=craigslist",
