        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Bedrooms:  1 Bathrooms:  1 Square Feet:  520 Date Available:  2026-05-27 Address:  1301 MN-7 Welcome to Brentwood Park, where comfort meets convenience! Our thoughtfully designed floor plans cater to a variety of lifestyles. Whether you're looking for a cozy one-bedroom or a roomy townhome, you'll find the perfect home to suit your needs. Explore our floor plans and discover why Brentwood Park is the ideal place to call home. Amenities Include: Controlled Entry System Playground Laundry Facility on Site Off-Street Parking Dog Park Extra Storage (Apartments) Easy Access to Public Transportation Pre-installed blinds Sleek Kitchen Finishes Divided sink Garages Optional Generous Sized Storage Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://thegoodmangroupliving.com/q6fhev6h/brentwood-park Pricing and availability are subject to change.A non-refundable application of fee of $45 is due at time of applying for apartment home. A non-refundable administration fee of $129 is due at time of move in. This community utilizes a Ratio Utility Billing Service (RUBS). Residents are responsible for payment of the following utilities: Electric, Gas, Water, Sewer, and Trash. Residents must pay a non-refundable RUBS billing fee of $4.08 per month, in addition to the resident’s portion of the property’s utilities for which resident is responsible.",
