        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Bedrooms:  2 Bathrooms:  1 Square Feet:  1092 Date Available:  2026-05-27 Address:  1301 MN-7 Welcome to Brentwood Park, where comfort meets convenience! Our thoughtfully designed floor plans cater to a variety of lifestyles. Whether you're looking for a cozy one-bedroom or a roomy townhome, you'll find the perfect home to suit your needs. Explore our floor plans and discover why Brentwood Park is the ideal place to call home. Amenities Include: Kitchen window for fresh air and views Controlled Entry System Sleek Kitchen Finishes Extra Storage (Apartments) Garages Optional Flex Rental Payments Available Open Courtyards and Grassy Areas Off-Street Parking Hopkins School District Easy Access to Public Transportation Full-size washer/dryer (Townhomes) Townhomes have 2 private entries Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://thegoodmangroupliving.com/xuuonn6a/brentwood-park Pricing and availability are subject to change.A non-refundable application of fee of $45 is due at time of applying for apartment home. A non-refundable administration fee of $129 is due at time of move in. This community utilizes a Ratio Utility Billing Service (RUBS). Residents are responsible for payment of the following utilities: Electric, Gas, Water, Sewer, and Trash. Residents must pay a non-refundable RUBS billing fee of $4.08 per month, in addition to the resident’s portion of the property’s utilities for which resident is responsible.",
