        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Spacious Room in Modern Vintage 3BR/1BA | $750/Month | 2704 Aldrich Ave S 2704 Aldrich Avenue South, Unit 1 (2704), 2704 | Room 2, Minneapolis, MN 55408 750.00 / Month 1 BEDROOMS | 1 BATHROOMS Interested? Fill out this form : https://renter.turbotenant.com/general-prescreener/T3duZXI6NzQ0NjEx?property=1449618&source=cl Have questions? Contact the Landlord : https://rental.turbotenant.com/p/2704-aldrich-avenue-south-minneapolis-mn-unit-unit-1- (2704)/5e619863-3f24-41dd-80df-a48a044dfd39?source=craigslist Property Description: Room for rent in a spacious vintage duplex with modern comforts & a relaxed vibe. Centrally located, this spot is cozy & ready to live in. Here’s what you’ll enjoy as a tenant: * Utilities Included (Water, Sewer, Trash, Internet)—only pay gas & electric. * High-Speed WiFi * Free In-Unit Washer & Dryer * Furnished Shared Spaces: Fully-equipped kitchen, cozy common room, bathroom * Free Street Parking The Perks: * Modern Appliances * Front & Back Patios * Free Monthly Cleaning Service This place is a walker and biker’s paradise! Aldi is 2 blocks away, Bob’s Java is <1 block away, & global dining options are at your doorstep, + a new Japanese restaurant down the block. Lake of the Isles is 10-min walk away. Interested? Check out our qualifications below. QUALIFICATIONS: Income Requirement: 3x monthly rent Security Deposit: $750 Renter's Insurance Required Credit Score: 660+ preferred Application Fee: $45 (background and credit check) Room Occupancy: 1 person limit No Pets, No Smoking Property Type : Multi Family Pets : No Pets Allowed Smoking : NO Lease Term : 750.00 / Month 750.00 Deposit Lease Length: Contact For Details Available: 07/01/2026 Occupancy Limit: 1 People Utilities Included : Cable Internet Garbage Sewage Water Appliances : Dishwasher Dryer Freezer Range Oven Microwave Refrigerator Washer Amenities : On Site Laundry Fenced Yard Lawn Near Parks Heating & Cooling : Baseboard Radiant Stove None 