        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post 110 E 1st St, Chaska, MN 55318 The studio, 1-, and 2-bedroom apartments at Zen Chaska are comfortably outfitted and ideally located, making us a great option for senior apartments in Chaska, MN. Find out what it’s like to spend less time in your car and more time in the places you love. Comfort is important, but peace of mind is priceless for senior living in Chaska, MN. At Zen Chaska, you'll enjoy both. Our thoughtfully crafted floor plans and extensive amenities cater to your every need, offering the home you've always desired. Step into a world of refined living, where each detail adds something to your life, and discover everything about the collection of our pet-friendly studio, one, and two-bedroom apartments. Apartment Features: Ceiling Fan Private Balcony Rentable Guest Suite Handrails Dishwasher Stainless Steel Appliances Window Coverings Hardwood Flooring Wheelchair Accessible Cable Ready Community Features: Package Receiving On-site Maintenance Availability 24 Hours Sundeck Clubhouse Accepts Credit Card Payments Garage Elevator Storage Flexible Rent Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://redtailliving.com/f5pzju2q/zen-chaska Pricing and availability are subject to change.",
