        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Bedrooms:  1 Bathrooms:  1 Square Feet:  605 Date Available:  2026-06-10 Address:  1301 MN-7 Welcome to Brentwood Park, where comfort meets convenience! Our thoughtfully designed floor plans cater to a variety of lifestyles. Whether you're looking for a cozy one-bedroom or a roomy townhome, you'll find the perfect home to suit your needs. Explore our floor plans and discover why Brentwood Park is the ideal place to call home. Amenities Include: Extra Storage (Apartments) Pre-installed blinds Laundry Facility on Site Generous Sized Storage Platinum Service Easy Access to Public Transportation Eat-in Kitchen Off-Street Parking Flex Rental Payments Available Garages Optional Dog Park Divided sink Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://thegoodmangroupliving.com/iuzgj7f4/brentwood-park Pricing and availability are subject to change.A non-refundable application of fee of $45 is due at time of applying for apartment home. A non-refundable administration fee of $129 is due at time of move in. This community utilizes a Ratio Utility Billing Service (RUBS). Residents are responsible for payment of the following utilities: Electric, Gas, Water, Sewer, and Trash. Residents must pay a non-refundable RUBS billing fee of $4.08 per month, in addition to the resident’s portion of the property’s utilities for which resident is responsible.",
