        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post 110 E 1st St, Chaska, MN 55318 The studio, 1-, and 2-bedroom apartments at Zen Chaska are comfortably outfitted and ideally located, making us a great option for senior apartments in Chaska, MN. Find out what it’s like to spend less time in your car and more time in the places you love. Comfort is important, but peace of mind is priceless for senior living in Chaska, MN. At Zen Chaska, you'll enjoy both. Our thoughtfully crafted floor plans and extensive amenities cater to your every need, offering the home you've always desired. Step into a world of refined living, where each detail adds something to your life, and discover everything about the collection of our pet-friendly studio, one, and two-bedroom apartments. Apartment Features: Hardwood Flooring Microwave Spacious Kitchen with Breakfast Bar Individual Climate Control Handrails Heat Air Conditioner Rentable Guest Suite Electric Range Refrigerator Community Features: Garage Sundeck On-site Maintenance Online Payments Available Library Storage Elevator Fitness Center Package Receiving Pets Allowed Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://redtailliving.com/ou7s3z7b/zen-chaska Pricing and availability are subject to change.",
