        "mainpic": "487de3de-5e30-4e45-b543-f5f148bcef44",
        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post A professional, mature (30+) single person is sought to rent a bedroom with a private bathroom in my home in Circle Pines. I recently moved into the house and am hoping to find one — or possibly two — good-natured people to share the space. The home has 4 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms across three floors, so there is plenty of room for privacy and comfort. A little about me: I’m an active professional in my late forties, originally from the UK, and I moved to Minnesota about 8 years ago. I lead a fairly quiet lifestyle and am looking for housemates who would enjoy and respect a calm, peaceful home environment. I welcome tidy, respectful, and considerate individuals of all backgrounds, ethnicities, and genders. This is a non-smoking home. I may also be open to a small pet with an additional $250 deposit. Applicants should be financially responsible and willing to complete a background and credit check. A landlord reference would also be appreciated. If interested, please send a little information about yourself, your work/lifestyle, and what you’re looking for in a shared home.",
